videos.description: Xavier Tillman Sr. flies to the rim to clean up Gabe Brown's miss with a putback slam vs. Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tillman rises for the follow slam) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Tillman rises for the follow slam

videos.description: Penn State guard Myreon Jones hits two consecutive 3-pointers vs. Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jones drains back-to-back 3s for Penn State) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Jones drains back-to-back 3s for Penn State

videos.description: Myreon Jones takes advantage of being left open and pulls up for a 3-pointer to knock in the Nittany Lions' tenth of the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jones sinks Penn State's 10th 3 of the half) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Jones sinks Penn State's 10th 3 of the half

videos.description: Rocket Watts blows by Penn State's defense for a tough layup at the rim and then on Michigan State's next possession he pulls up for a contested jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Spartans rookie hits pair of clutch shots out of the half) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Spartans rookie hits pair of clutch shots out of the half

videos.description: Michigan State's Aaron Henry fires a nice bounce pass under the hoop to Xavier Tillman Sr. who throws it down.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tillman drives in from the corner for a jam) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Tillman drives in from the corner for a jam

videos.description: Izaiah Brockington fires a slick pass in the paint to Lamar Stevens who finishes at the rim with a slam while absorbing contact.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stevens powers Penn State with and-1 jam) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Stevens powers Penn State with and-1 jam

videos.description: Lamar Stevens fakes out his Michigan State defender and pulls up for two while drawing a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stevens skillfully draws a foul while hitting tough jumper) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Stevens skillfully draws a foul while hitting tough jumper

videos.description: Aaron Henry drives through Penn State's defense and into the paint where he stops on a dime to fake out his defender before laying it in for two.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Henry stops short to fake out his defender for two) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Henry stops short to fake out his defender for two

videos.description: Cassius Winston helps Michigan State erase a 19-point deficit with a beautiful and-1 in the final minute vs. Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Winston's and-1 seals Michigan State's comeback) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Winston's and-1 seals Michigan State's comeback

videos.description: Cassius Winston and Tom Izzo don't see eye-to-eye during Michigan State's comeback win vs. Penn State on Tuesday.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Winston and Izzo jaw at one another during Michigan State’s win) 2020/3/3

videos.headline: Winston and Izzo jaw at one another during Michigan State's win
